  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/cb569574ed0db7b2f1b18337a0cf9731.poster.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/cb569574ed0db7b2f1b18337a0cf9731.webm?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/cb569574ed0db7b2f1b18337a0cf9731.mp4?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/9ef570263ceafa391a0706c25b441338.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=80 /></span><br><br>\"All that lives must die\". This ancient law has been successfully enacted by the Calcium Order for millennia. Until now. A strange serpentine creature refused, took hold of an island, and has been repelling the Order's agents rather successfully.<br><br>You have been summoned and contracted by the Order to solve the problem. You take your scythe and get on a boat.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A game that takes inspiration from fast-paced FPS classics from the '90s, but moves from there in its own slightly weird direction.<br></li><li>Fight through over 20 levels climbing the island's mountain to get to the lair of your contract target.<br></li><li>You have the unique weapons of the Calcium Order at your disposal. You'll find them somewhat familiar yet a bit otherworldly in form and function.<br></li><li>Learn your enemies' behaviors and use that knowledge in your deadly dance. Be warned, as some enemies can manipulate others to throw you off guard.<br></li><li>Mistakes happen. You can conveniently rewind time to any earlier point of the level or just jump back to a few seconds before your death.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/0e9af1ebded17d1ee86f87a430841661.poster.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/0e9af1ebded17d1ee86f87a430841661.webm?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eternal Harvest</h2><br>Eternal Harvest is a unique score-attack game mode in ever-changing procedural levels. It's a completely new and super fun way of enjoying Calcium Contract!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight your way through procedurally generated levels that rebuild themselves as you play!<br></li><li>Avoid or deliberately seek out Eternal Harvest curses. They increase your score but make the game harder in various quirky ways.<br></li><li>Compare your score to your friends and other players in the leaderboards.<br></li><li>Participate in daily challenges. A new challenge every day, but you only have one try!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/28b0191899fd72451d4259345a6d0f3c.poster.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/28b0191899fd72451d4259345a6d0f3c.webm?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/28b0191899fd72451d4259345a6d0f3c.mp4?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/cb569574ed0db7b2f1b18337a0cf9731.poster.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/cb569574ed0db7b2f1b18337a0cf9731.webm?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/cb569574ed0db7b2f1b18337a0cf9731.mp4?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/9ef570263ceafa391a0706c25b441338.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=80 /></span><br><br>\"All that lives must die\". This ancient law has been successfully enacted by the Calcium Order for millennia. Until now. A strange serpentine creature refused, took hold of an island, and has been repelling the Order's agents rather successfully.<br><br>You have been summoned and contracted by the Order to solve the problem. You take your scythe and get on a boat.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A game that takes inspiration from fast-paced FPS classics from the '90s, but moves from there in its own slightly weird direction.<br></li><li>Fight through over 20 levels climbing the island's mountain to get to the lair of your contract target.<br></li><li>You have the unique weapons of the Calcium Order at your disposal. You'll find them somewhat familiar yet a bit otherworldly in form and function.<br></li><li>Learn your enemies' behaviors and use that knowledge in your deadly dance. Be warned, as some enemies can manipulate others to throw you off guard.<br></li><li>Mistakes happen. You can conveniently rewind time to any earlier point of the level or just jump back to a few seconds before your death.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/0e9af1ebded17d1ee86f87a430841661.poster.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/0e9af1ebded17d1ee86f87a430841661.webm?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eternal Harvest</h2><br>Eternal Harvest is a unique score-attack game mode in ever-changing procedural levels. It's a completely new and super fun way of enjoying Calcium Contract!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight your way through procedurally generated levels that rebuild themselves as you play!<br></li><li>Avoid or deliberately seek out Eternal Harvest curses. They increase your score but make the game harder in various quirky ways.<br></li><li>Compare your score to your friends and other players in the leaderboards.<br></li><li>Participate in daily challenges. A new challenge every day, but you only have one try!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/28b0191899fd72451d4259345a6d0f3c.poster.avif?t=1773774508\" width=608 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/28b0191899fd72451d4259345a6d0f3c.webm?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427960/extras/28b0191899fd72451d4259345a6d0f3c.mp4?t=1773774508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
